<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. A Elysia pusilla 7 mm B Elysia cf. tomentosa 37 mm C Thuridilla cf. gracilis 18 mm D Colinatys sp. 3 mm E Aliculastrum cylindricum 30 mm F Aliculastrum debilis 28 mm G A. debilis (shell 12 mm) captured alive and predated by Haptosquilla cf. nefanda H Roxaniella multistriata 9 mm I Atys semistriatus 8 mm J Atys sp. 11 mm K Diniatys dentifer 5 mm L Diniatys dubius 6 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1042.64474.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/553100" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">Figure 6A</figureCitation>
